\\gamma p $ or $\\pi ^{-}p$ scattering\nnear-threshold energy region around $W\\simeq 11$ GeV are strongly suggested,\nwhich are accessible at COMPASS and JPARC. Particularly, the result of the\nphotoproduction suggests that it is very promising to observe the hidden-bottom\npentaquark at proposed EicC facility in China.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Dec 2019 01:58:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jul 2020 10:31:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-16"}
