ir robustness: 1) selective channel\nreplication which adds significantly less redundancy than used by the common\ntriple modular redundancy and 2) a fault-aware scheduling of processing\nelements for folded implementations\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Dec 2019 14:25:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-17"}
