 are now competing with other energy-harvesting\ndevices, such as thermoelectrics, over a large range of heat source\ntemperatures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Dec 2019 14:37:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-15"}
